{
  "stem": "11844.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now, I'd like you to know, by the way, that it was policy of Germany at that time that any Jew who left Germany and came back at that time automatically [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was thrown into a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the Dutch policeman did not let me in, but he got off his chair, left his office, and left the door open.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't realize what he was doing, but he said to me, get out of here.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I did not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It didn't even occur to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was very stupid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So half an hour, the next train, I go back to Germany, and what happens?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The same Stormtrooper looked at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You're back?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I told him yes, my papers were not in order right now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were not complete.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They couldn't let me in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I say, well, I go in the border city in a little hotel, and I called Holland right away and let them know where Amsterdam can send me the papers.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Stormtrooper said to me, I wouldn't do that because there are many [INAUDIBLE] at the border cities.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Why don't you go back to Heidelberg where you belong?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Inform the people in Holland where you are?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said to him, I can't because I have only 10 marks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He went in his pocket and gave me 20 or 30 marks, I forgot, enough for me to buy a ticket to go back to Heidelberg, and gave me his name.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Gramlich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I forgot his first name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he sent me back to Heidelberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am convinced that that's not the only time he did that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a decent, wonderful human being who saved my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
